            "chapterTitle": "Excellence of Standing in Prayer at Night",
            "urn": 1622080,
            "body": "<p>'Abdullah bin Mas'ud (May Allah be pleased with him) reported: Mention was made before the Prophet (\ufdfa) of a man who slept throughout the night till morning. The Messenger of Allah (\ufdfa) remarked, \"He is a man in whose ears Satan urinated.\"<br/><br/><b>[Al- Bukhari and Muslim]</b>.n<br/><br/></p>",
